CSSearchableItemAttributeSet

00:25:31.131 --> 00:25:33.000 align:middle line:-2
顺便说一下
如果你想要

00:25:33.066 --> 00:25:36.336 align:middle line:-2
把副标题赋给userActivity
也是同样道理 但此时

00:25:36.403 --> 00:25:40.307 align:middle line:-2
